trans-unit.source: Provides a reusable <xref href="System.Windows.Forms.UserControl"></xref> object for editing <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.ParameterCollection"></xref> objects.
trans-unit.target: Ger en återanvändningsbara <xref href="System.Windows.Forms.UserControl"> </xref> objektet för redigering <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.ParameterCollection"> </xref> objekt.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.ParameterCollectionEditor> class provides a user interface for editing the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Parameter> elements of <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ParameterCollection> objects that are referenced by several different properties of controls at design time.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.ParameterCollectionEditor>klassen innehåller ett användargränssnitt för redigering av <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Parameter>element i <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ParameterCollection>objekt som refereras av flera olika egenskaper för kontroller vid designtillfället.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ParameterCollection> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Parameter> </xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.ParameterCollectionEditor>

trans-unit.source: The ParameterEditorUserControl class encapsulates most of the functionality of the <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.ParameterCollectionEditor>.
trans-unit.target: Klassen ParameterEditorUserControl innehåller de flesta av funktionerna i <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.ParameterCollectionEditor>.</xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.ParameterCollectionEditor>

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.ParameterCollectionEditor> consists of an enclosing form that holds the ParameterEditorUserControl, and **OK** and **Cancel** buttons.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.ParameterCollectionEditor>består av en omslutande form som innehåller ParameterEditorUserControl och **OK** och **Avbryt** knappar.</xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.ParameterCollectionEditor>

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.ParameterEditorUserControl.AddParameters%2A> method adds an array of existing parameters to the ParameterEditorUserControl.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.ParameterEditorUserControl.AddParameters%2A>metoden lägger till en matris med befintliga parametrar i ParameterEditorUserControl.</xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.ParameterEditorUserControl.AddParameters%2A>

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.ParameterEditorUserControl.ClearParameters%2A> method removes all parameters from the ParameterEditorUserControl.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.ParameterEditorUserControl.ClearParameters%2A>metoden tar bort alla parametrar från ParameterEditorUserControl.</xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.ParameterEditorUserControl.ClearParameters%2A>

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.ParameterEditorUserControl.GetParameters%2A> method gets all parameters from the ParameterEditorUserControl.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.ParameterEditorUserControl.GetParameters%2A>metoden hämtar alla parametrar från ParameterEditorUserControl.</xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.ParameterEditorUserControl.GetParameters%2A>

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.ParameterEditorUserControl.SetAllowCollectionChanges%2A> method controls whether additions and deletions can be made to the parameters in the ParameterEditorUserControl.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.ParameterEditorUserControl.SetAllowCollectionChanges%2A>metoden kontrollerar om tillägg och borttagningar kan göras på parametrarna i ParameterEditorUserControl.</xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.ParameterEditorUserControl.SetAllowCollectionChanges%2A>

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.ParameterEditorUserControl"></xref> class using the specified <xref:System.IServiceProvider>.
trans-unit.target: Initierar en ny instans av den <xref href="System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.ParameterEditorUserControl"> </xref> klassen med hjälp av angivna <xref:System.IServiceProvider>.</xref:System.IServiceProvider>

trans-unit.source: The ParameterEditorUserControl constructor initializes the component controls of the <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.ParameterEditorUserControl> object, initializes UI elements, connects events for the individual component editors, and adds the component editors to the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.Control.Controls%2A> collection for the <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.ParameterEditorUserControl>.
trans-unit.target: ParameterEditorUserControl Standardkonstruktören component-kontroller av <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.ParameterEditorUserControl>objekt, initierar UI-element, ansluter händelser för enskild komponent-redigerare och lägger till komponenten redigerare i <xref:System.Windows.Forms.Control.Controls%2A>samlingen för <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.ParameterEditorUserControl>.</xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.ParameterEditorUserControl> </xref:System.Windows.Forms.Control.Controls%2A> </xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.ParameterEditorUserControl>

trans-unit.source: An <xref:System.IServiceProvider> interface to the current design host, such as [!INCLUDE[vsprvslong](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)].
trans-unit.target: En <xref:System.IServiceProvider>gränssnitt till den aktuella design värden som [!INCLUDE[vsprvslong](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)].</xref:System.IServiceProvider>

trans-unit.source: Adds an array of existing parameters to the editor.
trans-unit.target: Lägger till en matris med befintliga parametrar i redigeringsprogrammet.

trans-unit.source: The AddParameters method adds the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Parameter> elements of `parameters` to the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.ListView> control in the <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.ParameterEditorUserControl> object.
trans-unit.target: Metoden AddParameters lägger till den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Parameter>element i `parameters` till den <xref:System.Windows.Forms.ListView>Kontrollera i det <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.ParameterEditorUserControl>objektet.</xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.ParameterEditorUserControl> </xref:System.Windows.Forms.ListView> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Parameter>

trans-unit.source: If there is more than one <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Parameter> element, the AddParameters selects the first one in the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.ListView>.
trans-unit.target: Om det finns mer än ett <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Parameter>element i AddParameters väljer det första i <xref:System.Windows.Forms.ListView>.</xref:System.Windows.Forms.ListView> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Parameter>

trans-unit.source: Then the AddParameters refreshes the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.ListView> control and raises the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ParameterCollection.ParametersChanged> event.
trans-unit.target: Sedan AddParameters uppdaterar den <xref:System.Windows.Forms.ListView>kontroll och aktiverar den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ParameterCollection.ParametersChanged>händelse.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ParameterCollection.ParametersChanged> </xref:System.Windows.Forms.ListView>

trans-unit.source: A <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.Parameter"></xref> array of existing parameters to add to the editor.
trans-unit.target: En <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.Parameter"> </xref> matris med befintliga parametrar för att lägga till i redigeraren.

trans-unit.source: Removes all parameters from the editor.
trans-unit.target: Tar bort alla parametrar från redigeraren.

trans-unit.source: The ClearParameters method removes the parameters from the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.ListView> control in the <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.ParameterEditorUserControl> object.
trans-unit.target: ClearParameters-metoden tar bort parametrarna från den <xref:System.Windows.Forms.ListView>Kontrollera i det <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.ParameterEditorUserControl>objektet.</xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.ParameterEditorUserControl> </xref:System.Windows.Forms.ListView>

trans-unit.source: Then the ClearParameters refreshes the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.ListView> control and raises the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ParameterCollection.ParametersChanged> event.
trans-unit.target: Sedan ClearParameters uppdaterar den <xref:System.Windows.Forms.ListView>kontroll och aktiverar den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ParameterCollection.ParametersChanged>händelse.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ParameterCollection.ParametersChanged> </xref:System.Windows.Forms.ListView>

trans-unit.source: Gets all parameters from the editor.
trans-unit.target: Hämtar alla parametrar från redigeraren.

trans-unit.source: The GetParameters method populates a <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Parameter> array with all parameters from the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.ListView> control in the <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.ParameterEditorUserControl>.
trans-unit.target: Metoden GetParameters fyller i en <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Parameter>matris med alla parametrar från <xref:System.Windows.Forms.ListView>kontrollen i <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.ParameterEditorUserControl>.</xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.ParameterEditorUserControl> </xref:System.Windows.Forms.ListView> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Parameter>

trans-unit.source: A <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.Parameter"></xref> array of all parameters from the editor.

trans-unit.target: Styr om tillägg och borttagningar kan göras på värdena i redigeraren.

trans-unit.source: The SetAllowCollectionChanges method controls whether additions and deletions can be made to the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ParameterCollection> element in the <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.ParameterEditorUserControl> object.
trans-unit.target: Metoden SetAllowCollectionChanges styr om tillägg och borttagningar kan göras på den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ParameterCollection>element i den <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.ParameterEditorUserControl>objekt.</xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.ParameterEditorUserControl> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ParameterCollection>

trans-unit.source: The SetAllowCollectionChanges enables or disables the Up, Down, Add, and Delete buttons but it does not affect the editing of individual <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Parameter> elements.
trans-unit.target: SetAllowCollectionChanges aktiverar eller inaktiverar upp, ned, Lägg till och ta bort knappar, men det påverkar inte redigering av enskilda <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Parameter>element.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Parameter>

trans-unit.source: A <xref:System.Boolean> that indicates whether additions and deletions can be made to the <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.ParameterCollection"></xref> being edited.
